</atten4>
<step2>
<ptxt>Connect the intelligent tester to the DLC3.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C131977E05" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
</step2>
<step2>
<ptxt>Turn the ignition switch on (IG).</ptxt>
</step2>
